Deutonymph (collected at SA 9 and suspected to represent this species). Idiosoma L/W 303 / 229 ; integument dorsally lineated; muscle attachments unsclerotized; coxal field L 169 ; Cx-III W 199 ; Cx-I+II mL 47 , lL 104 ; provisional genital field with two pairs of Ac (
